y":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:07:50.000Z","msg":"Dq郭生+公職人員失當罪拘捕佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bd740a6c26fee99caa94ec001eb6e011276608","tid":1971970,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520554-20200414.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520554-20200414.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B84oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=7611c6a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520554-20200414.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2dabf20b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520554-20200414.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1520554_1_L_20200414170615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1520554_1_L_20200414170615.jpg&h=8afb2d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥下午6時在政府總部會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府下午7時將為傳媒安排「保就業」計劃的技術簡介會，勞工及福利局局長羅致光及政策創新與統籌辦事處總監馮程淑儀將會出席講解。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前推出第二輪防疫抗疫基金措施，涉及1375億元，當中包括向合資格僱主，提供為僱員的工資補貼。"},{"pid":"dcc9cdd402cce65fffb5422902c57abf3553efca","tid":1971970,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:09:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">專業議政稱第二輪防疫抗疫基金措施有不足</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本周五的立法會財委會會議將審議第二輪防疫抗疫基金撥款，專業議政認為措施有不足，例如已失業的人士或自由工作者未必受到支援。<br />\n<br />\n政府的措施包括補貼僱主應付工資，教育界議員葉建源舉例，不少私營幼稚園老師已被解僱，可能完全得不到支援，但這些人正是最需要協助。<br />\n<br />\n會計界議員梁繼昌說，專業議政建議當局設立失業援助金，例如市民如連續工作滿 3個月，但因疫情受解僱便可獲發一筆過援助金，金額可能是數萬元，認為可直接幫助有需要市民。<br />\n<br />\n梁繼昌又說，企業最大開支是薪酬與租金，一些業主因要應付按揭而不能減租，金管局應與銀行探討，能否在未來12個月讓業主只還息不還本。"},{"pid":"bb184fbb8f57f78df73a26dbeca176bf09b3eb7a","tid":1971970,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec6fda75543b25f8122c0e0baceb8e142fd2b13","tid":1971970,"uid":264074,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"佢GMT+8.2 6點2先會見人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"屌佢例牌遲到<br />\n仲AO出身喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f42bf8ea7937faa0f3ac2ee8c458af97c98a20d","tid":1971970,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"柒婆：我成功令疫情受控 開始清算醫護"},{"pid":"b742f7909488c722aa6b7c117559de35ec3e910e","tid":1971970,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"唔撚係烏江自刎就咪撚死出唻啦"},{"pid":"31731f2af574e00b774ef404131a9890890b7de9","tid":1971970,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68bd740a6c26fee99caa94ec001eb6e011276608","tid":1971970,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520554-20200414.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520554-20200414.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B84oeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=7611c6a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1520554-20200414.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2dabf20b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1520554-20200414.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1520554_1_L_20200414170615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1520554_1_L_20200414170615.jpg&h=8afb2d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥下午6時在政府總部會見傳媒。<br 